data.description: This charming home exudes warmth with beautiful wood floors, establishing a cozy and inviting ambiance. The open floor plan effortlessly connects the living and dining areas, making it ideal for hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, abundant cabinetry, and a small deck off the back, perfect for enjoying morning coffee.  A bonus room offers a well-designed laundry room and additional living space on the main level. Two spacious bedrooms share a well-appointed bathroom upstairs, ensuring comfort and convenience. The finished basement provides endless possibilities, serving as an additional living space for relaxation or entertainment. Just a block away from public transit as well as fantastic dining and shopping options, this home has it all!
